# Dataset root. Subfolders are created at runtime by tools/data_collector.py:
#   raw_cells/   - raw board-cell crops awaiting labeling
#   raw_shop/    - raw shop-slot crops awaiting labeling
#   labeled/     - sorted crops: labeled/<unit>_<star>/  (training set)
# calibration.json is also written here by `data_collector.py calibrate`.
